Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:11.26,中文,,0,0,0,,这里是市民Z在前线情报站北极光营地发回报告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is Citizen Z here at forward listening post Northern Light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.95,中文,,0,0,0,,北极光呼叫威尔逊山\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Northern Light to Mount Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.37,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山疾控中心 有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anyone from the Mount Wilson CDC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我有关于三角洲部队和咬痕组织\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have important information regarding Delta-Xray-Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.91,中文,,0,0,0,,的重要信息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and Operation Bite Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.17,中文,,0,0,0,,给点力啊 加利福尼亚 坚持住 你们的包裹就在路上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, California. Hang in there. Your package is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:26.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你们只需要去签收一下就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All you got to do is be there to sign for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:37.35,中文,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Gaaaahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.15,中文,,0,0,0,,这里是威尔逊山 我是海斯廷斯医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is Mount Wilson. This is Doctor Hastings at Mount Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:45.57,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了 威尔逊山 这里是北极光营地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes! Mount Wilson, you have Northern Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们被一大群第四阶段的感染者们攻击了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've been attacked by a swarm of level four infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的防线已经被攻破了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Our defenses have been breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.41,中文,,0,0,0,,逃生通道被高压电围栏封锁着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Our escape has been blocked by a high voltage fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.30,中文,,0,0,0,,从你的位置能进入电力网吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you access the power grid from your location?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能 我们到断路器的路上有太多僵尸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Negative. There are too many Zs between us and the breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.75,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我这边应该可以做些事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. I might be able to do something from my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.05,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我能进入\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I can access anything on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:05.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你们实验室的网络 它和外围围栏是由同一个发电机供电的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your lab network powered by the same generator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:06.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让它超载断电\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I might be able to overload it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.21,中文,,0,0,0,,切段围栏供电的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}knock out power to the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道密码\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:10.55,中文,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我们是国安局 无所不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're the NSA. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.63,中文,,0,0,0,,请快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:15.47,中文,,0,0,0,,好的好的 我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. All right. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经进去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm already in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.06,中文,,0,0,0,,额 威尔逊山\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uhhh, Mount Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们准备执行超载断电了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We are ready to execute overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:21.69,中文,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:23.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到你们的主机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm showing your mainframe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:24.98,中文,,0,0,0,,和基因测序装置都在同一个网络上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and gene sequencer on the same network.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那意味着你们在那台主机上存储的疫苗文件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That means any vaccine files that you have on that mainframe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:29.90,中文,,0,0,0,,都会被毁掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}are likely to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.32,中文,,0,0,0,,收到请指示\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please advise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.07,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山 我已经准备好超载停电了 请指示\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mount Wilson, I'm ready to execute overload. Please advise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.66,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我这么做 我会让你们的工作功亏一篑的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I do this, I'm going to fry your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你们有备份吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you have a backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.91,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mount Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.63,中文,,0,0,0,,这儿有太多僵尸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你必须把我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've got to get us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.16,中文,,0,0,0,,从这里弄出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:47.58,中文,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.72,中文,,0,0,0,,就是那样 快 快 快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's it! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.14,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托 威尔逊山 坚持住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, Mount Wilson. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.22,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(656,576)}{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fsp20}塔潘泽大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.68,中文,,0,0,0,,不管你在做什么 别停\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whatever you do, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.27,中文,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你觉得我会吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Haha, ya think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.08,中文,,0,0,0,,躲开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:16.66,中文,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.86,中文,,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,好技术\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nice driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.55,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh no. No-no. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.85,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.39,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我们没油了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, we're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.07,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 真有意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.23,中文,,0,0,0,,哈 哈 没油了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ha-ha. Out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,弹尽粮绝啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Running on fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.32,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你们好像爆胎了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So it looks like you got a flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.25,中文,,0,0,0,,大家小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Heads up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.31,中文,,0,0,0,,有人来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.98,中文,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:32.02,中文,,0,0,0,,继续开我们都会活着看到明天的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep rolling and we all live to see another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Let's do this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.03,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好像不是爆胎啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Doesn't look flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但是它不 转了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but it won't... turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我们碾过了些有趣的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We ran over some fun stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:54.29,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 帮我把它弄出来看看怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay. Well help me get it off and let's see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.89,中文,,0,0,0,,难怪车子一直向左偏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well that explains the pull to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:03.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.27,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了它 杀了它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kill it! Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.28,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 你 该回老家了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, you. Time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.24,中文,,0,0,0,,即使在经历了这些事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even after all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,它风景依旧美丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's still beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好好看一眼吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.25,中文,,0,0,0,,可能短时间内不会再回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Might be not back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.30,中文,,0,0,0,,再见 纽约\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So long New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,来生再见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See ya in the next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山 这里是北极光营地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mount Wilson, this is Northern Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.61,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山 这是北极光营地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mount Wilson, this is Northern Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.11,中文,,0,0,0,,快接\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.00,中文,,0,0,0,,威尔逊山 这里是市民Z\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mount Wilson, this is Citizen Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.12,中文,,0,0,0,,确认一下你们还在工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Making sure you're all still in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.75,中文,,0,0,0,,三角洲X光小队\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Delta-Xray-Delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.34,中文,,0,0,0,,三角洲X光小队\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Delta-Xray-Delta.
