Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.46,中文,,0,0,0,,有人收到吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does anybody copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.55,中文,,0,0,0,,有人收到吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does anybody copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:29.02,中文,,0,0,0,,咬痕组织根据地 咬痕组织根据地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Operation Bite Mark. Operation Bite Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.94,中文,,0,0,0,,您现在收听的是在所有已知的频率上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is Citizen Z from Camp Northern Light
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.64,中文,,0,0,0,,广播的北极光营地市民Z的直播\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}broadcasting live on all known frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.31,中文,,0,0,0,,即使没有多少人知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even a few nobody knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.81,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你有任何通讯方式 任何方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you have any way at all to communicate, any way at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.15,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你有短波 长波 暗波\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you've got short wave, long wave, dark wave,
