Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.99,中文,,0,0,0,,传声筒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}two cups and a string,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.99,中文,,0,0,0,,烟幕信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}smoke signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.82,中文,,0,0,0,,任何东西都可以 回应我一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anything. Just get back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我有卫星 我会看见的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've got a satellite. I'll see it.
