Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.16,中文,,0,0,0,,咬痕组织根据地 有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anyone from Operation Bite Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.50,中文,,0,0,0,,这里是北极光营地的市民Z\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is Citizen Z from Camp Northern Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我有一则关于加利福尼亚情况要向你们汇报更新\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have an update for you on the California situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得讨论一些可执行的方案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to discuss some operational realities.
