Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:09.98,中文,,0,0,0,,三角洲X光小队 收到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Delta-Xray-Delta, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信我跟所有人都失联了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't believe I lost everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.82,中文,,0,0,0,,那是狗拖的雪橇吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that a dog sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.69,中文,,0,0,0,,那是人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我 我觉得那是人类\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I... I think it's people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.66,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 谢天谢地 有人来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh thank god! Somebody's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,终于有人来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.50,中文,,0,0,0,,零食 他们会想要些零食的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Snacks! They're gonna want snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.53,中文,,0,0,0,,他们 他们会饿的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're... they'll be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.59,中文,,0,0,0,,得去打扫下浴室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got to clean up the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.70,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}People!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:42.46,中文,,0,0,0,,等下 是人还是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait. People or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所有这些车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All this cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,512)}{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fsp20} {\fad(0,100)}新泽西州 \N帕拉默斯公园购物中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.56,中文,,0,0,0,,竟然没有一滴油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And not a drop of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.11,中文,,0,0,0,,偏偏在这种我们以为是最糟糕的情况下 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just when you thought you saw the worst of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.78,中文,,0,0,0,,他们没有机会了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They didn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.28,中文,,0,0,0,,黑色星期五促销吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Black Friday sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你找到汽油了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You find any gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.73,中文,,0,0,0,,没 这个地方已经被清空了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. This area's been picked clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:08.65,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你在度假吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.57,中文,,0,0,0,,得有人保持记录\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Somebody has to keep record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我们可能是地球上最后一代人类了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know we're probably the last generations of humans on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.92,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们来说这是世界末日 她却觉得是美好回忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To us it's the apocalypse. To her it's the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:23.14,中文,,0,0,0,,要是我踢爆他的蛋蛋会损害到疫苗吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Would it hurt the antibodies if I kicked him in the nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what's your name, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.40,中文,,0,0,0,,一万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ten Thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.77,中文,,0,0,0,,那不是个名字 那是个数字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is not a name. It's a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.53,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的名字 我自创的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's my name. Made it up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:49.28,中文,,0,0,0,,想必也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well I suppose you'd have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.28,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么深意吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does it mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是我要杀的僵尸数量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How many zombies I'm going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.42,中文,,0,0,0,,那可是一大波僵尸啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well that's a whole lot of zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.51,中文,,0,0,0,,已经杀掉1055个了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Already on 1,055.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.59,中文,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.01,中文,,0,0,0,,杀够一万的时候要怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what happens when you get to 10,000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,改名\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Change my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.71,中文,,0,0,0,,改成什么 两万吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To what? Twenty thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.43,中文,,0,0,0,,杰夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢杰夫这个名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I like the name Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.86,中文,,0,0,0,,靠 闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.61,中文,,0,0,0,,人都去哪了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where did everybody go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.48,中文,,0,0,0,,除了那两个骑车的人我没看到其他幸存者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I haven't seen a survivor except for those two bikers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.03,中文,,0,0,0,,黑色夏天 人都饿死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Black Summer. Everybody starved to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,黑色夏天的时候我在费城\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was in Philly for Black Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那时很惨  我足足瘦了三十磅\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was bad. I lost thirty pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,还以为自己会死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.54,中文,,0,0,0,,那你是怎么活下来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How did you survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.33,中文,,0,0,0,,只要能生存 我无所不作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.00,中文,,0,0,0,,-嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,别开枪 不是僵尸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hold on. It's not a Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.34,中文,,0,0,0,,安静点 我没有被咬伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Peace. No bites here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.56,中文,,0,0,0,,百分之百正常活人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}100 percent alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你那朋友怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.95,中文,,0,0,0,,发现他有其他缺德朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Turns out he had other friends of low morals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.48,中文,,0,0,0,,抢走了我的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Took my ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,偷人车子 该被枪毙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Horse thieves should be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你该谨慎交友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should choose better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.24,中文,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能帮你什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What can we do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,一个人类和平小组能帮到一个单骑行人什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One peaceful group of humans to a lone traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.83,中文,,0,0,0,,能载我一程吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Could use a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.66,中文,,0,0,0,,单独一人可没法在外过夜啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure don't want to spend the night out here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.38,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不是做出租车生意的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We ain't running a taxi service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which way are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.97,中文,,0,0,0,,哪里都行 只要不回头就可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Any direction but back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:20.51,中文,,0,0,0,,听说有一大波僵尸在纽约南边活动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Word is there's a horde on the move south on the New York side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我瞧见你们在找汽油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I see you're scrounging for gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:27.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们常常说 掏钱搭车 没钱滚蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know like we used to say, ass, gas or grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.76,中文,,0,0,0,,就是不能白搭的意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nobody rides for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道在哪可以加满油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know where you could fill up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你最好告诉我们在哪里能加油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now would be the time to share that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:38.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那地方叫泽西魔鬼冶炼厂 大概五英里开外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Place called Jersey Devil Refinery, maybe five miles off,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.16,中文,,0,0,0,,下了高速公路就是了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just off the turnpike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道那有汽油的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How do you know there's gas there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.36,中文,,0,0,0,,尸毒爆发的第一天那里就被击溃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got overrun day number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.61,中文,,0,0,0,,油罐都是满的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All the tanks are still full,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.66,中文,,0,0,0,,都放着生锈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just rusting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.34,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 带我们去冶炼厂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, take us to this refinery
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.92,中文,,0,0,0,,如果那儿真如你所说的有汽油的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And if there's gas there like you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以搭我们的车去下一个哨站\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you can ride with us to the next outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你们不会白跑一趟的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You won't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你说对了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们出发霸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.43,中文,,0,0,0,,新人 我还有沃伦一辆车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}New guy's gonna ride with me and Warren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:09.55,中文,,0,0,0,,其他人上卡车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everybody else load up in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是不是以后我们每次停车的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So are we just gonna pick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.36,中文,,0,0,0,,都要捡上这些废物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}up every sketchy loser at every place we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们也把你带上了 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well we brought you along, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,再说了 也没人问过我的意见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Besides, nobody consulted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不会真的要和这个家伙一起去加州吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're not really going to California with this guy, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:29.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道世界末日就跟戒毒似的 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know the Apocalypse is a lot like rehab, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.99,中文,,0,0,0,,过一天算一天吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just take it one day at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.30,中文,,0,0,0,,该干啥就干啥吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then do the next indicated thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,现在这情况 就是要找到更多的汽油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In this case, that means get more gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.92,中文,,0,0,0,,跟着的事 谁知道啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}After that, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我们死定了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:21.77,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 如我们所料\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我们彻底没油了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're officially on E.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.61,中文,,0,0,0,,还有多远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.44,中文,,0,0,0,,就在前方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Spittin' distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.94,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,564)}{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fsp20} 新泽西魔鬼冶炼厂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.98,中文,,0,0,0,,这可不是冶炼厂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's not a refinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.53,中文,,0,0,0,,简直就是个僵尸厂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a zombie factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.21,中文,,0,0,0,,该死的僵尸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Frackin' zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他们好像迫切地想得到那边的什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They seem to want something in there real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是那个声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.21,中文,,0,0,0,,像蜜蜂闻见了花蜜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like bees to honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是僵尸闻见了尸臭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or Zs to shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.25,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿  你知道这些情况吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.69,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 反正易得的汽油都没有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, all the easy gas is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:45.17,中文,,0,0,0,,那么大家有什么高见吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what's the brilliant plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.98,中文,,0,0,0,,死掉 被吃掉 还是早早回家算了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Die, get eaten, go home early?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么味儿啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.09,中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸臭混合着汽油味\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The undead and gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.98,中文,,0,0,0,,都是非常易燃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Both highly flammable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.31,中文,,0,0,0,,所以绝对不能开火\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So no firearms of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.90,中文,,0,0,0,,那你想如何处理这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So how do you want to handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.60,中文,,0,0,0,,首先我们要让那个声音停下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well first we got to shut off whatever's making that noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.07,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 它可能是泵之类的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, it's probably some kind of pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.19,中文,,0,0,0,,但在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.27,中文,,0,0,0,,跟着那些僵尸走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Follow the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他们貌似都油罐家的最上边去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They all seem to be headed for the top of that tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我们去那儿看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll get up there and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们弄个声音把僵尸从油泵那引开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then we got to have a sound that draws the Zs away from the pump
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.20,中文,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能拿到汽油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so we can get to the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.29,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我把吉他留在蓝天营地了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, I left my guitar back at Camp Blue Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.62,中文,,0,0,0,,汽车喇叭声呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Car horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不行 他们会朝这来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, they'll all just head this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.62,中文,,0,0,0,,而且所有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And so will every
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.79,中文,,0,0,0,,能听见这声音的僵尸都会被引过来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}other dead head within earshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我有个办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.55,中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸都喜欢高调的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Zs like high-pitched sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.93,中文,,0,0,0,,越悦耳越好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The more musical the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.45,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 每天学到新东西啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wow, learn something everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你来当诱饵\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're our decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我和她一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我不需要他的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't need his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.14,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你需要掩护\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, you need cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.93,中文,,0,0,0,,带着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.46,中文,,0,0,0,,到架桥顶点时就开始放音乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And start the music when you get to the top of that catwalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你们两个 到另一侧的桥顶上去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You two, get to the top of the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.00,中文,,0,0,0,,看看是否可以停止那个声音 明白了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and see if you can kill that noise. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.55,中文,,0,0,0,,那个孩子去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where'd that kid go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.55,中文,,0,0,0,,他刚才还在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.14,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 他的名字是一万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh and his name is Ten Thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他最后能在我们要走时回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well he better be back by the time we're ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.02,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果我们能让发动那个油罐车 我们就能从那里加油 了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, if we get that tanker started and we could fill it up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.01,中文,,0,0,0,,那么多的汽油够我们开到加州了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}From the main tank, that much gas would get us to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你这个想法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I like the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那等下你们都被烧成灰的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what should I be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我该做些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}while you all are getting incinerated to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你带着同志先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, why don't you take Mr. Congeniality here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.32,中文,,0,0,0,,开着这辆萨博曼退回到安全地带\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the suburban and get back to a safe distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.69,中文,,0,0,0,,以防万一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.53,中文,,0,0,0,,如果 你知道 僵尸来了怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What if... you know... zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:36.53,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们都不幸出了事 那你就带他去加州\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If this all ends in tears, you got to get him to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.29,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.62,中文,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.93,中文,,0,0,0,,等一下 伙计 等一下 我会帮你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait one second, buddy. Wait one second. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.77,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们来给你暖和一下吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, let's warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.55,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 外面很冷 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh yeah, it's cold outside, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.27,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 好孩子 好孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Good boy. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.17,中文,,0,0,0,,要疯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.65,中文,,0,0,0,,森夏恩 等等我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sunshine! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 慢点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你会害死我们两的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're gonna get us both killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.94,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上我们两中只有一个会死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually just one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你要做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know what you're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.66,中文,,0,0,0,,没用的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你对我一无所知\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't know anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道托拜厄斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know Tobias
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,家族的其他人员不会让你走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the rest of the family is never gonna let you leave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,森夏恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我永远都不回去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well I'm never going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.96,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 我不是森夏恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And my name isn't Sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.51,中文,,0,0,0,,那个女孩早就死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That girl died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.46,中文,,0,0,0,,没有你我回不去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't go back without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.19,中文,,0,0,0,,这可不是对家人该有的态度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's no way to treat family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.14,中文,,0,0,0,,艾迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.81,中文,,0,0,0,,听着  我就是不相信墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, I just don't trust Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好吗 他有点不对劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay? There's something wrong with that dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.70,中文,,0,0,0,,他可不是有点疯而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's more than just a little crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,整个任务简直就是异想天开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This whole mission is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.49,中文,,0,0,0,,沃伦和加内特可不这么认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Warren and Garnett don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.74,中文,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德为了保护他而死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hammond died trying to protect him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,还有很多人都为他牺牲了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and so did a lot of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你也要这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want to do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.99,中文,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.05,中文,,0,0,0,,但如果这是真的呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What if it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,如果墨菲真的是他们所说的那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What if Murphy's who they say he is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:48.97,中文,,0,0,0,,如果真的有机会制造疫苗呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and there's a chance for a vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.50,中文,,0,0,0,,世界末日已经来临 没救了 艾迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't get a do-over on the end of the world, Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.17,中文,,0,0,0,,已经太晚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.05,中文,,0,0,0,,就算只有一丝机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If there's the slightest chance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.30,中文,,0,0,0,,能够唤醒我记忆中的世界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of waking up in the world I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.18,中文,,0,0,0,,让逝者安息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where dead things stay dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我都要牢牢抓住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a chance I'm gonna take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.34,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是希望 麦克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cuz that's hope, Mack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我已经多久没有那种感觉了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know how long it's been since I've felt something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,那不是希望 是谎话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not hope. It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.60,中文,,0,0,0,,会害死我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it's gonna get us both killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,那我宁愿在谎言中死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well then I'd rather die believing in a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.86,中文,,0,0,0,,也不愿毫无信念的活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than live believing in nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你说大道理的时候真他妈性感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damn, you're sexy when you get all philosophical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,继续转\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep cranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.58,中文,,0,0,0,,转出来的能量都够供给一座小城市了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cranking enough to light up a small city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.70,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.25,中文,,0,0,0,,试试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.21,中文,,0,0,0,,还来 快点 车快没油了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, hurry up. It's almost running out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.21,中文,,0,0,0,,再坚持一会就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.54,中文,,0,0,0,,他们一旦停掉了噪音我们就赶紧走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get ready to go as soon as they kill that noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.77,中文,,0,0,0,,快点 真酷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on. That was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.31,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 这个坏家伙就是问题所在啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. This bad boy's the problem all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:50.31,中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸最喜欢火和噪音了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing zombies like more than fire and noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.06,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊，还有人脑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, except brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么关掉它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How do we turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,制动按钮坏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well the stop button doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.07,中文,,0,0,0,,这个肯定是靠压力操作的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Must operate on pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,得弄个减压阀之类的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like some kind of relief valve or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.66,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以把它卡主\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe we can jam it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.29,中文,,0,0,0,,要不试试用压力或是它排放的任何气体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well what about the pressure or whatever it's venting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,可以 但我们没时间四处找了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, we don't hang around to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.46,中文,,0,0,0,,拿到油就要赶紧跑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get the gas and get out of dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只是需要东西把它卡住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We just need something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.25,中文,,0,0,0,,像是棍子或者什么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to jam it up with like a pole or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.67,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我爱这个东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No! I love this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.67,中文,,0,0,0,,快想办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.98,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.80,中文,,0,0,0,,那些僵尸涌上来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what happened to all the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.23,中文,,0,0,0,,之后会怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}zombies that have been coming up here? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:30.77,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.54,中文,,0,0,0,,他们成功了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 准备好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们该走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.55,中文,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.35,中文,,0,0,0,,幸好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.56,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们知道这些僵尸都怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now we know what happened to the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.98,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我们真该走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, it's really time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.18,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道那边怎么样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wonder how it's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.98,中文,,0,0,0,,还没听到什么爆炸声呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Haven't heard anything blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:52.98,中文,,0,0,0,,还没有呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:54.90,中文,,0,0,0,,八\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.65,中文,,0,0,0,,抓牌吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.09,中文,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.10,中文,,0,0,0,,现在真的该走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now it's really time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:27.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我在这里 宝贝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你去哪里了 小家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where'd you go, fella?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我在这呢 宝贝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:40.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:45.97,中文,,0,0,0,,快过来 小狗狗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come here, doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.04,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.87,中文,,0,0,0,,找到你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:07.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 宝贝 要喝点水吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How are you, boy? Do you want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.75,中文,,0,0,0,,渴了吗 好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you thirsty? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.50,中文,,0,0,0,,来这边 喝点水吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come here. Let's get some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.22,中文,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:16.89,中文,,0,0,0,,渴了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你渴了吗 宝贝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you a thirsty boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.43,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:27.68,中文,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样 快喝 哥儿们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, that's right. Drink up, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:28.93,中文,,0,0,0,,快喝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:32.52,中文,,0,0,0,,狗狗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.74,中文,,0,0,0,,狗狗 回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dog, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:38.83,中文,,0,0,0,,狗狗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.25,中文,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 上面什么情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nice job. What was up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.17,中文,,0,0,0,,气压啊 阀门啊 之类的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Some kind of a pressure valve thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.59,中文,,0,0,0,,那个池子里全是僵尸 满满的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But that tank is full of zombie goo, like to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,真迷人 持续不了多久 同志们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Beautiful. It ain't gonna hold, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.26,中文,,0,0,0,,放音乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Start the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:54.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我们扭起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:16.73,中文,,0,0,0,,祝我们好运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我去拿油管\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got the hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.50,中文,,0,0,0,,拿过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:42.09,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:46.43,中文,,0,0,0,,开始进油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Firing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:58.27,中文,,0,0,0,,第一次知道钓鱼游戏里也可以出老千\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First time I've ever seen anybody cheat at go fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:23:59.66,中文,,0,0,0,,这是天赋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:01.91,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么特么要这么久\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell is taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.83,中文,,0,0,0,,如今的加油服务已经没有当初那么周到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Full service just ain't what it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.20,中文,,0,0,0,,放轻松\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:08.00,中文,,0,0,0,,加内特和沃伦没有问题的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Garnett and Warren know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:11.75,中文,,0,0,0,,周围僵尸太多了 我屎都快吓出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Too many Zs around here. It's freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:12.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我有僵尸恐惧症\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got a phobia
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:16.12,中文,,0,0,0,,自从我被咬了之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you know ever since I got bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:20.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直想问问你 被咬了之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've been meaning to ask you about that. So these bites...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:24.30,中文,,0,0,0,,慢着 你算是哪门子医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait. What kind of doctor are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:28.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是真正的医生 更像是业余的药剂师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not really a doctor, more of an amateur pharmacologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:31.39,中文,,0,0,0,,那你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.44,0:24:35.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么会成为人类的救星的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How'd you get to be the savior of the human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.15,0:24:36.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的想知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.70,0:24:41.45,中文,,0,0,0,,真相就是我过去一直被冤枉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Truth is for a guy who's been wrongly convicted,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:43.40,中文,,0,0,0,,其实我充满了正义之感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm actually very civic-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.45,0:24:45.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我是志愿被实验的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.16,0:24:48.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你们抓错人了 我什么都没做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got the wrong guy. I didn't do nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.91,0:24:51.99,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 试验证明我不适合啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, I'm being denied my due process, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.04,0:24:53.38,中文,,0,0,0,,放我走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我是无辜的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm innocent, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.96,0:24:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,放我走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:25:01.34,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然很难 可必须有人这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It wasn't easy, but somebody had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.05,0:25:03.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你被选中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have been selected
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:03.89,中文,,0,0,0,,成为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for exposure
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,疫苗实验者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to an experimental...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.31,0:25:09.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我天 除非他们狠狠地揍我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Man, they would have to beat me senseless,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:10.76,中文,,0,0,0,,把我敲晕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}strap me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.81,0:25:12.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我才可能让他们在我身子里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before I'd ever let anybody inject me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.52,中文,,0,0,0,,注入新鲜刚出炉的僵尸病毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}with a live zombie virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.57,0:25:16.82,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不能只为了我自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, well it wasn't about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.85,0:25:20.07,中文,,0,0,0,,有些事你必须去做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know you do what you got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.11,0:25:21.69,中文,,0,0,0,,为了我们的下一代\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}For the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.19,0:25:27.33,中文,,0,0,0,,之后你打了疫苗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you... you got the vaccine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.36,0:25:28.70,中文,,0,0,0,,然后就被咬了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then you got bitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.70,0:25:29.83,中文,,0,0,0,,整整八次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eight times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.87,0:25:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,哎哟我天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.25,0:25:32.53,中文,,0,0,0,,是说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:34.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那一定很恐怖吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That must have been horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.20,0:25:36.87,中文,,0,0,0,,应该吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Must have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.92,0:25:41.18,中文,,0,0,0,,幸运的是我晕过去了 啥都记不起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Luckily I blacked out, so I don't remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.21,0:25:44.38,中文,,0,0,0,,不知咋地哈蒙德救了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Somehow Hammond rescued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.38,0:25:46.55,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然晚了点 总比没救好 我觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Better late than never, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:48.30,中文,,0,0,0,,之后就一直在逃命了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And been on the run ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.35,0:25:50.89,中文,,0,0,0,,现在哈蒙德也死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now Hammond's dead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.77,0:25:54.77,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 真是美好的时光啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yep. Good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:55.72,中文,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:25:58.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们多了些吵闹的邻居\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got some nosey neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.36,0:25:59.81,中文,,0,0,0,,- 去叫别人 - 别吸引他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Call the others! - You're attracting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.86,0:26:01.23,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们要出去 - 闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Get us out of here! - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.62,0:26:06.90,中文,,0,0,0,,真棒啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.95,0:26:08.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你朋友们的油箱一满\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your friends tank up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.32,0:26:10.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就可以把他们的汽油再弄过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and we take it from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.66,0:26:11.99,中文,,0,0,0,,可不是我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There is no we .
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.04,0:26:13.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我不会回去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.88,0:26:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,死也不会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.08,0:26:17.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要抗拒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why do you keep fighting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.00,0:26:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道他不会放你过你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know he's never gonna let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:24.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我会想一切办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will do whatever I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.05,0:26:27.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'll do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.42,0:26:30.26,中文,,0,0,0,,去告诉你的新朋友们我是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell your new friends who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.26,0:26:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉他们你是谁 会怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happens when I tell them what you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.98,0:26:39.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不 神啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.65,0:26:41.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我勒个去啊 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good grief, dude
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.10,0:26:41.90,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲 没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.94,0:26:43.35,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲 墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.41,0:26:44.77,中文,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.82,0:26:45.91,中文,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:47.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你在这里很安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're safe in here man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:49.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他们进不来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They can't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.20,0:26:51.45,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你保持冷静就可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now just try to breathe through it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.45,0:26:52.20,中文,,0,0,0,,呼吸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.25,0:26:53.45,中文,,0,0,0,,他们就在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right there. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.45,0:26:56.79,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 够了 听着 外面就两个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, that's enough. Look, there's only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.79,0:26:57.92,中文,,0,0,0,,听着伙计 我现在要出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look man, I'm gonna go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.95,0:26:59.67,中文,,0,0,0,,把他们赶跑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm gonna draw them away
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.71,0:27:01.26,中文,,0,0,0,,让他们尝尝我的厉害\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I'm gonna mercy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.29,0:27:03.51,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你只要冷静一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now you just... just chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.38,0:27:11.52,中文,,0,0,0,,为啥事情都这么麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why is nothing ever easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.81,0:27:22.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 跟我来 小家伙们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, follow me boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.53,0:27:24.98,中文,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.98,0:27:27.65,中文,,0,0,0,,新鲜的肉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fresh meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.90,0:27:31.32,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 好家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.75,0:27:45.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.42,0:27:46.42,中文,,0,0,0,,注意听\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:27:58.35,中文,,0,0,0,,到车子里去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get in the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.35,0:27:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:50.85,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 嘿 孩子 嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Hey, boy! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.35,0:29:30.72,中文,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.67,0:30:04.64,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 蠢货\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.67,0:30:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他不好吃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.97,0:30:08.26,中文,,0,0,0,,他味道不咋地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's all chewed up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.26,0:30:11.43,中文,,0,0,0,,来啊 朋友 过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, friend. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.43,0:30:14.26,中文,,0,0,0,,抬起下巴 让医生来检查下子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Raise your chin for your ol' pal Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.65,0:30:20.02,中文,,0,0,0,,别慌 墨菲 他们进不去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hang in there, Murphy! They can't get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:41.68,中文,,0,0,0,,第1058个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One thousand fifty eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.71,0:30:43.01,中文,,0,0,0,,把他们弄走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.04,0:30:44.46,中文,,0,0,0,,把他们弄走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.52,0:30:49.22,中文,,0,0,0,,第1059个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One thousand fifty nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:59.56,中文,,0,0,0,,第1060个 射得漂亮 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One thousand sixty! Nice shot, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.70,0:31:02.61,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.98,0:31:07.15,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 罗伯塔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.15,0:31:08.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这该死的油管我拿不下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't get this damn hose off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.71,0:31:19.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.56,0:31:30.67,中文,,0,0,0,,下去 下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.57,0:31:38.52,中文,,0,0,0,,下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.87,0:31:56.87,中文,,0,0,0,,那个是墨菲吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that Murphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.87,0:31:57.83,中文,,0,0,0,,真是不幸啊 还真是他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unfortunately, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.60,0:32:15.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们走 我们走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out of here. Get out of here! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.80,0:32:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.69,0:32:18.81,中文,,0,0,0,,慢着 你要干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait a minute. What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.86,0:32:22.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我要去救墨菲 快 快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got to save Murphy. Come on. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:42.55,中文,,0,0,0,,滚开 特拉维斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out of my way, Travis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.58,0:32:44.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想杀你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't want to have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.47,0:32:49.14,中文,,0,0,0,,没有问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's not gonna be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:57.09,中文,,0,0,0,,该回家了 森夏恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's time to go home, Sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.41,0:33:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,想都别想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.78,0:33:13.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我逃惯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.20,0:33:15.95,中文,,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.60,0:33:42.76,中文,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.82,0:33:46.43,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:48.15,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.08,0:33:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.13,0:34:02.05,中文,,0,0,0,,放开他 混蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get off of him you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.09,0:34:03.09,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:12.90,中文,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.34,0:34:18.55,中文,,0,0,0,,不许你碰这一年来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not gonna kill the only living thing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:21.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我见到的唯一生物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've seen in a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.89,0:34:34.69,中文,,0,0,0,,快 你快出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Come on! Got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.74,0:34:35.94,中文,,0,0,0,,不 外面僵尸太多了 我不出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No! There's too many! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.99,0:34:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,快出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.69,0:34:37.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.52,0:34:38.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我不出去 不能出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.44,0:34:38.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我动不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.03,0:34:40.11,中文,,0,0,0,,可以的 现在不是害怕的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes! It is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 我不出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No! No! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:41.53,中文,,0,0,0,,车子马上就要爆炸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.58,0:34:42.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:43.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我动不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.12,0:34:48.95,中文,,0,0,0,,电影里都是一下就打晕了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This works easier in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.93,0:35:01.51,中文,,0,0,0,,第1062个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One thousand sixty two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.55,0:35:03.05,中文,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.66,0:35:39.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.59,0:35:48.23,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.26,0:35:51.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你 你还活着 不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're... You're still alive. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:59.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.41,0:36:06.86,中文,,0,0,0,,好棒 尝到我的厉害了吧 疯狗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah! Yeah, take that Cujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.86,0:36:08.70,中文,,0,0,0,,就是要这个样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's what I'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.17,0:36:13.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我们做到了 小狗狗 我和你 我们做到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We did it, pup. Me and you, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.70,0:36:16.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.76,0:36:21.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.40,0:36:43.12,中文,,0,0,0,,就你和我 小狗狗 就你和我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's just you and me, pup. Just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.57,0:36:52.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我找到了牛肉饼和牛肉三明治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, I've got beef patty and sloppy joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.22,0:36:58.11,中文,,0,0,0,,看起来你比较喜欢吃牛肉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You look like a beef eater to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:36:58.69,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.72,0:36:59.86,中文,,0,0,0,,开饭啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.89,0:37:03.19,中文,,0,0,0,,这其实是我经历过的最棒的约会了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is actually one of the best first dates I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.23,0:37:07.56,中文,,0,0,0,,开饭喽 看起来很好吃吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here we go. Oh yeah, doesn't that look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.28,0:37:10.07,中文,,0,0,0,,喔 慢慢吃 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa. Slow down, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.12,0:37:12.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我只有十年的库存\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I only have ten year supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.91,0:37:14.96,中文,,0,0,0,,伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.99,0:37:17.79,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 这不是个好名字 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hmmm. That's not a very good name, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.83,0:37:22.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以想个更好的 那个伙计 怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nah, we can do better than that, can't we? What about 'the dude?'
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:24.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢 那个伙计 这部电影\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I really like that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:28.14,中文,,0,0,0,,不喜欢 好吧 我们还可以想个更好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No? Yeah, we can come up with something better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.17,0:37:29.09,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 好小子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:34.09,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.10,0:37:39.73,中文,,0,0,0,,看起来有人在玩儿火呀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Looks like somebody's been playing with matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.76,0:37:41.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那里是什么 炼油厂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is that? Is that a refinery?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:47.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们找到汽油了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So did we get the gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.91,0:37:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,真不错 谁搞砸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great. Who screwed that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.91,0:37:59.12,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 不好意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.17,0:38:02.09,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 你的朋友在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.45,0:38:07.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他死了 而且他不是我的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He didn't make it. And he wasn't my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.27,0:38:23.72,中文,,0,0,0,,哈罗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.73,0:38:26.03,中文,,0,0,0,,哈罗 是我 北极光营地的市民Z\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello. It's me, Citizen Z from Northern Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.06,0:38:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,请问你是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To whom am I speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.53,0:38:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,查理加内特警官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sergeant Charlie Garnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.23,中文,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.28,0:38:31.62,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴能和你说话 长官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good talking to you again sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.65,0:38:32.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你那儿怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.95,0:38:34.20,中文,,0,0,0,,马马虎虎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:36.07,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 那个包裹怎样呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Excellent. And the package?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.12,0:38:37.29,中文,,0,0,0,,还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.32,0:38:39.74,中文,,0,0,0,,请告诉我把他带到哪儿去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please tell us where to drop him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.74,0:38:41.04,中文,,0,0,0,,加州\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}California.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.08,0:38:43.33,中文,,0,0,0,,加州 等等 不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}California? Wait. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.38,0:38:44.80,中文,,0,0,0,,慢着 那是不可能的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hold on. That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.83,0:38:47.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要去更近的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to go some place closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,更近 额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Closer? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.05,0:38:52.97,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 警官 不能再近了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry Sergeant, but there is no... closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.00,0:38:54.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我们和管事儿的说话吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I speak to someone in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:38:58.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 收到 我确定他们也很想跟你说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, copy that. I'm sure they'd like to talk to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.43,0:39:00.84,中文,,0,0,0,,但有点困难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But that may be a little problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.90,0:39:02.23,中文,,0,0,0,,有点困难是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you mean problematic?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.26,0:39:04.31,中文,,0,0,0,,一大波僵尸正在靠近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}More puppies and kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:05.73,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么不能和实验室的人说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why can't I speak to somebody at the lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:06.90,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧长官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.93,0:39:08.52,中文,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.57,0:39:11.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们失联了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've lost contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.57,0:39:12.69,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们还活着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are they even still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.74,0:39:15.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我正在努力确认中 长官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm working on confirming that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.94,0:39:20.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我在屏幕上看到一大波僵尸正在向你们靠近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've got a screen full of incoming Zs headed your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.28,0:39:21.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你最好采取行动了 军士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'd better get moving, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.67,0:39:24.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我能找到你 但现在 一直往西走到海边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll find you. But for now, go west till you hit the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.59,0:39:29.87,中文,,0,0,0,,哈罗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.92,0:39:31.76,中文,,0,0,0,,加内特警官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sergeant Garnett?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.79,0:39:33.93,中文,,0,0,0,,警官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.85,0:39:36.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 可他们是咱们的唯一希望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know. But they're the only chance we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.69,0:39:44.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我要来电音乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.90,0:39:53.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以的 好小子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, we can. Yeah, that's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.07,0:40:02.41,中文,,0,0,0,,看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.46,0:40:04.91,中文,,0,0,0,,帅呆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.96,0:40:10.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为再也见不到这玩意儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Never thought I would see this thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.97,0:40:13.22,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 小孩儿来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait! Here comes the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:14.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我找到这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Found these.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.30,0:40:15.34,中文,,0,0,0,,小家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:16.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你简直是上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.75,0:40:18.81,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们要抓紧了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah well hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.50,0:40:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,打扰一下 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.95,0:40:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你头发里有根手指\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have a finger in your hair.
